StringLiteralExpr.value: Must enter at least observation vector ''Series''.
Activation function ''ActiveFN'' must be a string.
Activaton function ''ActiveFN'' must be TANH, LOGISTIC, or FUNFIT
Maximum orders ''maxOrders'' must a vector of 3 positive integers.
Observation ''Series'' must have at least %d obeservations.
Significance level ''Alpha'' must be a scalar.
Significance level ''Alpha'' must be between 0 and 1.
Regressions type ''FLAG'' must be a string.
